orture and enhanced interrogation of enemy combatants, and the American carceral state.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 3.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aWar crime trialszGuamxHistoryy20th century. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xAtrocitieszGuam. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDuke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311069632540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478090236zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478090236/original  a978-3-11-069632-5 Duke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA